<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="vl18Oct1927"><font color="red">ca. 18 October 1928</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Valery Larbaud): I have just finished revision of Anna Livia for transition no 8. What a job! 1200 hours of work on 17 pages. She has grown &mdash; riverwise &mdash; since the night you heard her under the sign of Ursa Minor. Her fluvial maids of honour from all ends of the earth now number about 350 I think. </div>
